	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64641268"><p>All I can say is sorry young people.  A few of us tried, but it was like being Don Quixote surrounded by CO2 spewing Windmills.  I commuted by bicycle.  The roads were I lived, though a bit dangerous, did not compare to how bad roads are in other parts of the US.</p></div>
